OL,3,CHow late Bipolar disorder diagnoses
OL,4,Cchanged mine and Angela Rayner's life
OL,6,FITV News Deputy Political Editor
OL,7,FAnushka Asthana and Labour Deputy
OL,8,FLeader Angela Rayner sat down in April
OL,9,Fto discuss how Bipolar disorder has
OL,10,Fshaped their lives
OL,12,F"It's just nothing. It's just pain...
OL,14,F"She can't move... She doesn't want to
OL,15,Flive.
OL,17,F"It's just real, deep, deep sorrow."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/21
