OL,3,CHow late Bipolar disorder diagnoses
OL,4,Cchanged mine and Angela Rayner's life
OL,6,FI was sitting opposite Labour's deputy
OL,7,Fleader, Angela Rayner, in the middle
OL,8,Fof an interview quite different to
OL,9,Fthose I would normally be expected to
OL,10,Fcarry out.
OL,12,FWe were not sparring over workers'
OL,13,Frights or questions of tax and
OL,14,Fproperty. Instead, in this
OL,15,Fconversation for ITV News, she was
OL,16,Fdescribing the sheer depths of
OL,17,Fdepression suffered by her mum.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/21
OL,2,W/*%+.!/*%/"-$ /*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,
