OL,3,CHow late Bipolar disorder diagnoses
OL,4,Cchanged mine and Angela Rayner's life
OL,6,FIn between painful anecdotes,
OL,7,Fincluding the anger she sometimes felt
OL,8,Fas a child, Rayner kept reminding me
OL,9,Fhow proud she was of Lynn Bowen. "Even
OL,10,Fin her darkest hours, she tried her
OL,11,Fbest," she said.
OL,13,FBowen suffered with Bipolar disorder,
OL,14,Fand ever since I heard Rayner talk
OL,15,Fabout it, on the Leading podcast with
OL,16,FAlastair Campbell and Rory Stewart,
OL,17,FI'd been desperate to discuss it with
OL,18,Fher myself. There was one thing she
OL,19,Fsaid that made me stop in my tracks.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/21
OL,2,W/*%+.!/*%/"-$ /*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,
