OL,3,CHow late Bipolar disorder diagnoses
OL,4,Cchanged mine and Angela Rayner's life
OL,6,FThrough him I met others with Bipolar
OL,7,FDisorder too, who would try to
OL,8,Fdescribe the sheer disconnection of
OL,9,Fthe psychosis they experienced -
OL,10,Farguing that their highs could trigger
OL,11,Fbehaviour just as life-threatening as
OL,12,Ftheir suicidal lows.
OL,14,FAt one point, I witnessed the sharp
OL,15,Fend of mental health services,
OL,16,Fimmediately followed by the most
OL,17,Fcritical side of physical health
OL,18,Fprovision - and I was shocked by what
OL,19,FI saw. The gulf between the two when
OL,20,Fdealing with similarly serious
OL,21,Fconditions felt extreme.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/21
