OL,3,CHow late Bipolar disorder diagnoses
OL,4,Cchanged mine and Angela Rayner's life
OL,6,FIn one case it took a week to see a
OL,7,Fconsultant - in the other, we received
OL,8,Fthat level of care within just minutes.
OL,10,FWhen I wrote a letter of complaint to
OL,11,Fthe mental health unit after my
OL,12,Fbrother died, they called me in for a
OL,13,Fmeeting.
OL,15,FI walked nervously to the end of a
OL,16,Fplain, clinical corridor and sat
OL,17,Fopposite them, behind a desk.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/21
OL,2,W/*%+.!/*%/"-$ /*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,
