OL,3,CHow late Bipolar disorder diagnoses
OL,4,Cchanged mine and Angela Rayner's life
OL,6,FI told them I was shocked by the lack
OL,7,Fof provision. To my surprise, they
OL,8,Fagreed and pointed to my job (back
OL,9,Fthen chief political correspondent at
OL,10,Fthe Times).
OL,12,F"You are a journalist; can't you write
OL,13,Fabout it?"
OL,15,FIn truth, I've not felt able to talk
OL,16,Fabout my brother until now, but
OL,17,Fsomething in Rayner's interview made
OL,18,Fme change my mind. Maybe my experience
OL,19,Fcould help me highlight some of these
OL,20,Fissues.
