OL,3,CHow late Bipolar disorder diagnoses
OL,4,Cchanged mine and Angela Rayner's life
OL,6,FHave you heard our new podcast Talking
OL,7,FPolitics? Every week Tom, Robert and
OL,8,FAnushka dig into the biggest issues
OL,9,Fdominating the political agenda...
OL,11,FIn the decade since that happened,
OL,12,Fthere has been a lot of talk about
OL,13,Fparity of esteem between physical and
OL,14,Fmental health, but I still see many of
OL,15,Fthe same challenges. Bipolar UK tell
OL,16,Fme that over a million people live
OL,17,Fwith this illness in Britain, and yet
OL,18,Fit still takes, on average, 9.5 years
OL,19,Fto get a diagnosis.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/21
