OL,3,CHow late Bipolar disorder diagnoses
OL,4,Cchanged mine and Angela Rayner's life
OL,6,FBowen also struggled to read and
OL,7,Fwrite, resulting in her once bringing
OL,8,Fhome a can of dog food that she
OL,9,Fthought was stewing steak - and,
OL,10,Fanother time, shaving foam instead of
OL,11,Fcream.
OL,13,FI ask about any regrets she might have
OL,14,F- as I know I have plenty, and then
OL,15,Fturn to that delay in diagnosis,
OL,16,Fwondering - would my brother be here
OL,17,Fif he'd had that information ten years
OL,18,Fearlier?
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G13/21
OL,2,W/*%+.!/*%/"-$ /*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,
