OL,3,CHow late Bipolar disorder diagnoses
OL,4,Cchanged mine and Angela Rayner's life
OL,6,F"My mum spent weeks in hospital when
OL,7,Fshe didn't need to be in hospital. If
OL,8,Fshe had got the intervention early on,
OL,9,Fand the support early on, she would
OL,10,Fnot have ended up in that crisis
OL,11,Fpoint," admitted Rayner.
OL,13,FSameer Jauhar - one of the country's
OL,14,Fleading experts on Bipolar disorder,
OL,15,Fsaid one of the big problems is that
OL,16,Fthe delay in diagnosis can stretch
OL,17,Ffrom the late teens to the early
OL,18,Fthirties - a critical time in which
OL,19,Fpeople are developing relationships
OL,20,Fand life.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G14/21
OL,2,W/*%+.!/*%/"-$ /*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,
