OL,3,CHow late Bipolar disorder diagnoses
OL,4,Cchanged mine and Angela Rayner's life
OL,6,F"The rates of self-harm, suicide are
OL,7,Ftremendously increased," he said -
OL,8,Fadding that the treatment for Bipolar
OL,9,Fdepression differs from other forms.
OL,11,FOne mistake can be giving a person
OL,12,Fwith Bipolar - antidepressants that
OL,13,Fcan actually drive their mania.
OL,15,FBut with an early diagnosis, he said
OL,16,Fthere were now effective treatments
OL,17,Fand interventions.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G15/21
OL,2,W/*%+.!/*%/"-$ /*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,
