OL,3,CHow late Bipolar disorder diagnoses
OL,4,Cchanged mine and Angela Rayner's life
OL,6,FThat is why he is suggesting much
OL,7,Fearlier screening for Bipolar and even
OL,8,Fthe use of AI to scour medical records
OL,9,Fto look for clues.
OL,11,FHow one quick diagnosis changed one
OL,12,Fman's life
OL,14,FSam Swidzinski was a teenager when he
OL,15,Fstarted to realise that something was
OL,16,Fnot right.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G16/21
