OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F313A1715866590
OL,3,CHow late Bipolar disorder diagnoses
OL,4,Cchanged mine and Angela Rayner's life
OL,6,F"I had no concept... that could lead
OL,7,Fto a negative consequence."
OL,9,FInstead, sitting opposite Sameer in
OL,10,Fthe KCL canteen, Sam credits the
OL,11,Fleading psychiatrist with saving his
OL,12,Flife.
OL,14,FWith treatment, he was able to study
OL,15,Fpsychology and is now working with
OL,16,FSameer as he completes a PhD on
OL,17,FBipolar.
OL,19,FSam said those interventions put him
OL,20,Fback on track. And relationships?
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G20/21
